##### TO CLOSE THE COUNCIL.

The same precautionary steps precede the Closing as precede the Opening
of a Council of the Illustrious Order of the Red Cross.

<span id="img_note0"></span> ![](img/note0.jpg)

The Sovereign Master, in his discretion, may hold Rehearsal of Duties
before closing.

