##### PRAYER

O LORD our God, we thank thee, we praise thee, we magnify thee for the
gift of thy holy Light. Make it to shine into our hearts, and write thy
Law upon our consciences.

And now as we go out into, the world again may the words of our mouths,
and the meditations of our hearts, be acceptable in thy sight, O Lord,
our strength and our redeemer. <span class="smallcaps">Amen</span>!
Response, <span class="smallcaps">Amen</span>!

<span id="img_starsep"></span> ![](img/starsep.jpg)

